  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><h1><style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t\t<!--td {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 1px solid #ccc;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tbr {\n\t\t\t\tmso-data-placement: same-cell;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t-->\n\n\t\t</style><span data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15171,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":16777215},\"9\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":5987163},\"15\":\"\\\"Open Sans\\\"\",\"16\":12}' data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Welcome to the Go! Go! Nihon and Akamonkai Online Japanese Course. We have created this beginner crash course for those who have yet to start language school in Japan.\"}' style=\"font-size: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Welcome to the Go! Go! Nihon and Akamonkai Online Japanese Course!</strong></span></span></h1><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"fr-video fr-fvc fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"https://platform.thinkific.com/videoproxy/v1/play/bqpptmuhra84otn7q0rg\" scrolling=\"no\" class=\"videoproxy_embed\" title=\"DavideV2.mp4 - 00:16\" name=\"videoproxy_embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t\t<!--td {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 1px solid #ccc;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tbr {\n\t\t\t\tmso-data-placement: same-cell;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t-->\n\n\t\t</style></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Go! Go! Nihon &amp; Akamonkai Japanese Language school have developed this 12-week online beginner course to help you understand the basics of Japanese<b>, prepare for JLPT N5&nbsp;</b>and complete 150 hours of study.</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><style type=\"text/css\"><!--td {border: 1px solid #ccc;}br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}--></style><span data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15171,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":16777215},\"9\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":5987163},\"15\":\"\\\"Open Sans\\\"\",\"16\":12}'>After completing the course, you will find yourself in a much better position to start at an intensive Japanese Language School school or continue your studies with further courses, knowing these essential basics.&nbsp;</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><h3><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><strong>Other reasons why you might like this course</strong></span>&nbsp;</span></span></h3><ul><li style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">You studied in Japan before and you want to refresh your knowledge</span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Your plan to study in Japan was cancelled but you still want to learn Japanese</span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li style=\"margin-bottom:1em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">You want to see if studying Japanese in Japan is right for you, starting with taking this course</span>&nbsp;</span></span></li></ul><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><a href=\"https://gogonihon.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more about studying Japanese in Japan here</a></span>&nbsp;</span></span></p><h2><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><strong>What is the best way to learn from this course?</strong></span>&nbsp;</span></span></h2><ol><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><span data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15171,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":[null,2,16777215],\"9\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":[null,2,3553613],\"15\":\"Arial\",\"16\":12}' data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"1. Practise for at least 30 minutes per day outside of class\"}'><strong>Practise</strong> for at least 30 minutes per day outside of class.</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><span data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15171,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":[null,2,16777215],\"9\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":[null,2,3553613],\"15\":\"Arial\",\"16\":12}'><strong>Do the exercises and all your homework.</strong> It&#39;s important to keep up with the pace and do your assignments by the set deadline.</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><span data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15171,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":[null,2,16777215],\"9\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":[null,2,3553613],\"15\":\"Arial\",\"16\":12}'><strong>Use subtitles.&nbsp;</strong>Lesson videos have captions in both English and Japanese, practice with and without them to build up your skills</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><strong>Join the <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/communities/Q29tbXVuaXR5LTM1MzQ=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Japanese Beginner Course Community</strong></a>.</strong> You can share your opinion, ask questions and practice with the other students of our online community<em>.</em></span>&nbsp;</span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><strong>Try to enjoy your time.</strong> It can be challenging learning online and some days you might not have the motivation. Try to remember why you want to learn Japanese and make the most of this experience. &nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</span></span></li></ol><p><span data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":15171,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":[null,2,16777215],\"9\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":[null,2,3553613],\"15\":\"Arial\",\"16\":12}' data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"4. Try to enjoy your time. It can be challenging learning online and some days you might not have the motivation. Try to remember why you want to learn Japanese and make the most of this experience.\"}' style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"><span data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":31555,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":16777215},\"9\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":5987163},\"15\":\"\\\"Open Sans\\\"\",\"16\":12,\"17\":1}' data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Note: All lessons in this course are divided by sections (weeks). An introductory section called \\\"Welcome to the course!\\\" and the first week of the course will be available from the start. The following weeks will be accessible on a weekly basis. So, week 2 will start one week after beginning the course and so on!\"}'><strong>Note</strong>:&nbsp;</span></span>&nbsp;</span><span data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":31555,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"4\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":16777215},\"9\":0,\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"14\":{\"1\":2,\"2\":5987163},\"15\":\"\\\"Open Sans\\\"\",\"16\":12,\"17\":1}' data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Note: All lessons in this course are divided by sections (weeks). An introductory section called \\\"Welcome to the course!\\\" and the first week of the course will be available from the start. The following weeks will be accessible on a weekly basis. So, week 2 will start one week after beginning the course and so on!\"}' style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><em><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">All the lessons in this course are divided by days. There are also two introductory sections called &quot;Course introduction&quot; and &quot;Welcome to the course!&quot;&#39; plus a final section called &quot;next steps&quot;.&nbsp;</span></em>&nbsp;</span> </span></p></div>",
